Invocation Name: pushup challenge
des:
Ever wished you could do 100 pushups at once? With this new Alexa skill all you need is a few minutes each day and in a month you will be stronger than ever. This skill will track your progress over a month, offering support and encouragement so you can reach your goals. Development is ongoing so please leave a review for features you would like to see added. Currently working on adding multiple difficulty levels and a leaderboard system.

If you are looking for a quick 5 minute challenge instead check out our new 5 minute pushup skill! With an engaging narrator to keep you pumped you will master your pushup skills and improve your strength with only 5 minute sessions - https://www.amazon.com/dp/B078Z5QMH7
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
